    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been meticulously maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, making it a very reliable choice for its next owner. While the exterior paint still holds a great shine, there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean and well-preserved, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that presents well and is ready to drive home today.",
