    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and sophistication. This unit remains in commendable condition, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic excellence. It offers a refined driving experience, balancing robust engineering with a well-preserved interior. A premier choice for the discerning motorist seeking a reliable, high-caliber automotive asset.",
      "price": 34900.0,
