    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly a dream to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and it runs like a champ. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32000.0,
