      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional traction and corner-exit dynamics. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by a McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension arrangement. While the exterior shows minor road-going wear, the engine's compression is consistent, and the throttle mapping remains sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
